version_description: Added ticket notification reminder
Added multiple reminders notes.
Added distance in miles (also in km), as requested by users.
Augmented reality added to help you to find your location. Also the radar is a new awesome feature added.
Flurry has been added. Augmented reality accuracy improved.
Added preview video in iTunes and minor improvements.
Minor improvements added.
Accuracy parameters improved.
Tutorial regarding how to manage the app.

More improvements in V4.0:
Added Share location button with the screenshot of the location saved.
Added nice color background in the footnote of the location saved.
New feature added! The users can find also nearby free parking slots.

Your parking lot is saved automatically.
